<li id="cite_note-Auer-2017-29">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Auer-2017_29-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Auer-2017_29-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Auer-2017_29-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFAuer2017" class="citation journal cs1">Auer, Matthew R. (2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/48722942">"Rescuing the decision process"</a>. <i>Policy Sciences</i>. <b>50</b> (4): <span class="nowrap">519–</span>526. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1007%2Fs11077-017-9292-2">10.1007/s11077-017-9292-2</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.worldcat.org/issn/0032-2687">0032-2687</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/48722942">48722942</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:254899402">254899402</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Policy+Sciences&amp;rft.atitle=Rescuing+the+decision+process&amp;rft.volume=50&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=519-526&amp;rft.date=2017&amp;rft.issn=0032-2687&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A254899402%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F48722942%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1007%2Fs11077-017-9292-2&amp;rft.aulast=Auer&amp;rft.aufirst=Matthew+R.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F48722942&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHarold+Lasswell" class="Z3988"></span></span>
